metadata.name: wings sunin
metadata.description:
Hello, I'm Grow, a webtoon artist.

In the first half of this year, a webtoon called 'Soul of Bari' is planned to be serialized at an independent serialization site for a long time.
At the same time, we plan to publish an NFT that shares the webtoon and worldview.

I hope webtoons and NFTs become a virtuous cycle.

It is good that writers working in independent serials can continue their serializations through NFT sales,
I hope that those who have purchased NFT will also be able to steadily increase its value through long-term webtoons.

When the webtoon is serialized, I will link the site address to the profile.

Please pay a lot of attention.
